west coast lhc theory meeting hfsaf logo west coast lhc theory home registration participant list agenda location travel information accommodations dinner event contact welcome to the west coast lhc theory meeting december 9 2011 kavli auditorium slac national accelerator laboratory menlo park california registration is free please register by november 30 2011 the purpose of these meetings is to encourage theorists in the west coast region to collaborate and pool resources and expertise as we confront the problems raised by the physics results from the lhc each meeting has features lectures on common theme this meeting will feature four lectures on the general subject of new particle searches beyond 5 fb 1 in the afternoon we will have a session devoted to contributed papers from the participants we especially encourage graduate students to submit short contributions we hope you will have a stimulating day at slac michael peskin for the wclhctm steering committee announcements please reserve your room early at stanford guest house registration is free please register by november 30 2011 register now reserve accommodations your browser does not have the ability to display inline frames you can view the content of this frame at this page slac footer privacy statement
